## Generator

- 推荐主脑不要手写任务包，而是先运行：
  - `bash scripts/make_task_packet.sh --role <role> --task <task_id>`
- packet 既可以贴给另一个会话，也可以直接作为 `codex exec` 的 stdin 输入。
- 推荐的半自动派单顺序是：
  - `bash scripts/doctor.sh --target <dir>`
  - `bash scripts/main_brain_summary.sh --target <dir>`
  - `bash scripts/list_open_tasks.sh --open-only`
  - `bash scripts/dispatch_task.sh --task <task_id> --owner <owner>`
  - dispatch 会通过 `task.dispatched` callback 自动补 feedback skeleton
  - `bash scripts/show_task.sh --task <task_id>` if main brain wants the current audit summary before or after dispatch
  - `bash scripts/process_callbacks.sh --latest`
  - `bash scripts/list_history.sh --task <task_id>` when main brain needs the timeline instead of raw json/jsonl files
  - `bash scripts/check_worker_feedback.sh --task <task_id>`
  - `bash scripts/close_task.sh --task <task_id> --to review|done`
  - `bash scripts/submit_feedback.sh --task <task_id> --with-retrospective` only when feedback needs repair or retrospective needs manual initialization
- 如果要走 exec worker 路径，建议顺序是：
  - `bash scripts/exec_healthcheck.sh --target <dir>`
  - `bash scripts/run_exec_worker.sh --task <task_id> --owner <owner> --target <dir>`
  - `bash scripts/process_callbacks.sh --latest --target <dir>` if you need to replay the newest callback deterministically
  - `bash scripts/show_task.sh --task <task_id> --target <dir>` before deciding close/reopen/cancel
  - `bash scripts/check_worker_feedback.sh --task <task_id> --target <dir>`
  - `bash scripts/check_retrospective.sh --task <task_id> --target <dir>` if the run initialized a retrospective
  - `bash scripts/close_task.sh --task <task_id> --to review|done --target <dir>`
- 如果要一次并行跑多个 write-scope 不冲突的 exec workers，可运行：
  - `bash scripts/run_exec_batch.sh --tasks <task1,task2,...> --owner-prefix exec --target <dir>`
- 如果默认 task slot 太宽、batch 预检会冲突，可给 batch 增加：
  - `--lock <task_id:path>`
- `scripts/run_exec_worker.sh` 只负责 claim/packet/feedback init/`codex exec`/last-message 落盘，不会自动 close task。
- `scripts/process_callbacks.sh` 只执行受控 built-in actions，不会把任务自动推进到 `done`。
- 如果多个 worker 对同一个 task 留下了不同 artifact，推荐先运行：
  - `bash scripts/adjudicate_task.sh --task <task_id> --target <dir>`
- `adjudicate_task.sh` 默认只比较 worker 主证据；callback/event artifacts 作为附加证据，不进入默认 comparison surface。
- `bash scripts/main_brain_summary.sh --target <dir>` 适合主脑先看全局，再决定哪些 task 需要审计、裁决或收口。
- 这套脚本是半自动 orchestration convenience layer，不是后台自动调度器。
